The '''Royal Hangar''' was the official [[Starship/Legends|starship]] [[Hangar/Legends|hangar]] of the [[Queen Mother]] of the [[Hapes Consortium/Legends|Hapes Consortium]].

It was connected to the [[Queen Mother's Special Salon]] in the [[Fountain Palace]] on [[Hapes/Legends|Hapes]]. When [[Han Solo/Legends|Han Solo]] and [[Leia Organa Solo/Legends|Leia Organa Solo]] arrived on Hapes in [[40 ABY/Legends|40 ABY]], they were allowed to land the [[Millennium Falcon/Legends|''Millennium Falcon'']] there.

During the [[Battle of Kashyyyk (Second Galactic Civil War)|Battle of Kashyyyk]], when Han and Leia returned to warn the Queen Mother about [[Darth Caedus|Jacen's]] atrocities, they were followed by [[Tahiri Veila]], who attempted to arrest them as traitors. Leia and Tahiri [[Duel in the Royal Hangar|dueled]] briefly until Tenel Ka arrived with her guards. Tahiri was arrested, and, in spite of her protests, her [[StealthX wing]] was confiscated and she was shuttled off-world by the [[Hapan]]s.

